# Update Contact Avatar

    PUT services/:service_id/contacts/:contact_id/avatar
    
Updates a [Contact]'s avatar for the specified Service and returns the updated object





## Parameters
### URI Parameters
None
### Body Parameters
Field | Data Type | Required | Description
--- | --- | --- | ---
content_type | string | Y | The type of file that is being uploaded
base64 | string | Y | A base64 encoding of the image to be uploaded

## Example
### Request

    PUT https://api.zingle.me/v1/services/aff7bc93-6e28-4e70-8770-defa35cdfc1b/contacts/f119fe3b-67e2-4b59-b605-5586616978d0/avatar


#### Request Body    
```json
{
  "content-type": "image/png,
  "base64": ""
}
```
